- Update to version 26.3.3 (from 25.12.0):
  * V1 programmatic API and schema subcommand
  * Parameterized execution environment initialization
  * EEConfig dataclass for structured EE configuration
  * Custom EE build tags and definition filenames
  * SCM server support for private Git repositories
  * Registry TLS verification control (--registry-tls-verify)
  * Runtime-configurable EE workflows via dispatch inputs
  * Replaced hardcoded hub URLs with generic galaxy_servers
  * Python 3.12 interpreter for AAP 2.5 compatibility
  * Fixed ansible_core/ansible_runner exclusion for base images 

